    <item>
      <title>美元走强、收益率上升导致新兴市场货币跌至 2024 年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/emerging-market-assets-sink-to-2024-low-amid-growth-rate-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球最大经济体降息时间的不确定性，美元上涨，发展中国家货币指标跌至去年 11 月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/emerging-market-assets-sink-to-2024-low-amid-growth-rate-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 08:18:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列誓言做出回应，欧洲天然气消除了年初至今的损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/european-gas-jumps-as-israel-vows-response-to-iran-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列高级军事官员重申，他们的国家别无选择，只能对伊朗周末的袭击做出反应，因此，由于担心中东冲突更广泛升级，欧洲天然气价格消除了今年的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/european-gas-jumps-as-israel-vows-response-to-iran-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 07:05:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
